### Create text job
POST http://localhost:4000/api/jobs/text
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: demo-user

{
  "prompt": "블로그 내용을 요약해 주세요.",
  "params": {
    "tone": "friendly"
  }
}

### Create image job
POST http://localhost:4000/api/jobs/image
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: demo-user

{
  "prompt": "대담한 타이포그래피의 YouTube 썸네일",
  "params": {
    "size": "1024x1024"
  }
}

### Get job
GET http://localhost:4000/api/jobs/seed-text

### Retry job
POST http://localhost:4000/api/jobs/seed-text/retry
